  <ul><li>Image Optimization: Add concise, descriptive ALT text to meaningful images.</li></ul>
  <h3>Long-Term SEO Strategy: 30-90 Days</h3>
  <ul><li>URL Structure: Use short, lowercase, readable URLs with hyphens and minimal parameters.</li><li>Meta Description: Rewrite the description to stay close to 140-160 characters.</li><li>Breadcrumbs: Add visible breadcrumbs and BreadcrumbList schema on deeper pages where hierarchy matters.</li><li>Image Optimization: Use lazy loading for below-the-fold images.</li><li>Image Optimization: Serve WebP or AVIF where practical and compress large images.</li><li>Text to HTML Ratio: Reduce unnecessary markup and ensure meaningful crawlable text is present.</li><li>Google Tag Manager: Add GTM if tag management is required, or document the alternative implementation.</li><li>Blog Presence: Create or expose an SEO-focused content section if organic content growth is a priority.</li></ul>

